      "url": "http://www.thedevopscourse.com/devops/work",
      "page": "the devOps ways of work",
      "sentence": "(Hayek, 179)He goes on to write:In sports or in examinations, no less than in the world of government contracts or prizes for poetry, it would clearly be pointless to arrange for competition, if we were certain beforehand who would do best..."
