      "url": "http://www.thedevopscourse.com/devops/work",
      "page": "the devOps ways of work",
      "sentence": "But it turns out that most successful software projects, over many decades, instead followed the \"UNIX philosophy\", where development projects sought to quickly achieve an MVP, and then proceeded to improve that initial product with incremental changes."
