      "url": "http://www.thedevopscourse.com/devops/work",
      "page": "the devOps ways of work",
      "sentence": "The advantages of small improvements to a software product, released frequently, include:Value is delivered to the users quickly, rather than waiting for \"release 2.0\" for the users to get a hold of the features they need."
