      "url": "http://www.thedevopscourse.com/devops/work",
      "page": "the devOps ways of work",
      "sentence": "There may be regulatory/legal requirements for the software that the users interviewed by the analysts simply took for granted, the violation of which will only become apparent when those users are faced with a working version of the software."
