      "sentence": "So that the minimum state would consist of four or five men.\u201d And Adam Smith famously expounded upon those benefits in The Wealth of Nations, writing \u201cThe greatest improvement in the productive powers of labour, and the greater part of the skill, dexterity, and judgment with which it is anywhere directed, or applied, seem to have been the effects of the division of labour\u201d (The Wealth of Nations)."
