      "sentence": "Eliot, \"Choruses from the Rock\" Lesson 3: DevOps and the Division of LaborMy talk at StackOverflowLeonard E. Read began his famous essay \u201cI, Pencil\u201d (here) by noting:I, Pencil, simple though I appear to be, merit your wonder and awe, a claim I shall attempt to prove\u2026 Simple?"
