      "page": "the devOps ways of work",
      "sentence": "But, when ten workers took on specialized tasks, with the help of specialized machinery, though \u201cthey were very poor, and therefore but indifferently accommodated with the necessary machinery, they could, when they exerted themselves, make among them about twelve pounds of pins in a day\u201d (same source), with the result that each worker produced several thousand times the number of pins per day as would have been possible without the division of labor."
