      "url": "http://www.thedevopscourse.com/devops/work",
      "page": "the devOps ways of work",
      "sentence": "Programmers cannot do their jobs in isolation: thus, the practice of continuous integration, which quickly exposes mutual misunderstandings of how one person\u2019s work impacts that of others."
